fields.title: Nigerian Green Frankincense
fields.display_title: Nigerian Green Frankincense – Premium Quality Aromatic Resin, Hand-Sorted, Sustainably Harvested, Natural Incense for Meditation, Energy Cleansing & Spiritual Rituals – 100g
fields.details:
Discover the rare and powerful AL ZAHR Nigerian Green Frankincense, a premium grade aromatic resin known for its pure citrusy aroma, uplifting energy, and spiritual benefits. Carefully hand-sorted and sustainably harvested, this elite resin is sun-cured to perfection, ensuring the highest quality for incense burning, energy cleansing, and spiritual rituals.

Nigerian Green Frankincense is treasured worldwide for its bright, clean fragrance and ability to enhance meditation, prayer, and relaxation practices. It burns with a refreshing aroma that clears negative vibes, promotes mental clarity, peace, and positivity, and serves as an ideal component for luxury incense blends and aromatic resin formulas.

Whether used for daily rituals, meditation, or simply to uplift your space with its natural fragrance, AL ZAHR Nigerian Green Frankincense offers a truly authentic aromatic experience.

fields.title: Mallow Leaf | Dried Molokhia

Bring natural wellness and greenery into your home with Al Zahr Pure Raw Mallow Leaf (Dried Molokhia) – 250g. Hand-sorted and sustainably packed, these 100% natural and non-GMO herbal plant seeds are perfect for organic cultivation, herbal gardens, and traditional herbal applications.

The mallow leaf, also known as Molokhia, is treasured for its rich nutritional value, gentle flavor, and versatile uses — from herbal infusions to soil enrichment and organic gardening. Packed in a durable, reusable plastic jar, this product reflects Al Zahr’s commitment to purity, sustainability, and freshness — making it an essential addition for every gardener and herbal enthusiast.

fields.title: Long Pepper Whole Spice
fields.display_title: Long Pepper Whole Spice | Premium Quality Whole Spice for Home Garden, Planting & Cultivation | Hand-Sorted, High Grade, 100% Pure Seeds – 100g
fields.details:
Experience authentic spice cultivation with AL ZAHR Long Pepper Whole Spice — a premium-grade whole spice ideal for home gardening, planting, and herbal cultivation. Each 100g pack contains hand-sorted, 100% pure, high-quality long pepper seeds, known for their rich aroma and distinctive flavor.

 

Native to tropical regions, Piper Longum—also known as Indian Long Pepper or Pippali—is a versatile spice plant valued for both culinary and medicinal purposes. Whether you’re a home gardener or spice grower, these seeds offer a rewarding and aromatic growing experience.

 

Cultivate the essence of ancient spice tradition with AL ZAHR Long Pepper Seeds—pure, potent, and perfect for your organic garden.
